<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-48-0475 </DOCNO><TEXT>Equilibrium distributions of charged and neutral particles in limitedplasma-molecular systems with an arbitrary configurations of boundariesare calculated with all multipole expansion terms taken into account.The distributions of free and bound particles in the case of semi-limitedsystems that have harmonic oscillators or rigidly coupled pairs of chargedparticles as a molecular subsystem are studied in detail. 39 refs.; 6figs.</TEXT></DOC>